<emphasis box="[249,569,1932,1956]" italics="true" pageId="28" pageNumber="679">Philodendron inaequilaterum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
ocurrs in the semideciduous and evergreen forests of Cerro Pirre, between 90 and 
<specimenCount box="[251,329,1999,2023]" pageId="28" pageNumber="679" type="generic">
<quantity box="[251,325,1999,2023]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="8.0" pageId="28" pageNumber="679" unit="m" value="800.0">800 m</quantity>
